data.title: Category:Maria Luisa, Duchess of Lucca
data.text:
Maria Luisa of Spain (Maria Luisa Josefa Antonietta Vicentia; 6 July 1782, – 13 March 1824) was a daughter of Charles IV of Spain. She married Louis of Bourbon-Parma and was Queen of Etruria and later Duchess of Lucca.
